name: TT-9
Lore: 'Auxiliary mobilization supply transport. Coordinates with the Droid Control Ship to determine whether additional STAPs are needed in any given area. Enclosed.',
Text: 'May add 4 passengers and 3 STAPs. Once per turn, may deploy a STAP to same site from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Immune to attrition < 3 (< 5 if your AAT or STAP present).',
